reviewText: sent it to a friend as a gift and he opened it and there wasn't even a DVD inside. Pretty angry and embarrassed

Ehh,..Not so great. I learned maybe 1 or 2 moves in this video. I am looking more for a fighting style that involves street fighting. In the real world you have to worry about ppl doing unexpected things like biting. I do not want my leg over a persons mouth in a real fight. This fighting style is great for fighting in a ring, but not so much in a street fight where anything goes.
MMA sambo Vol. 1 w/ herv Geldman is awesome. It is really an inspiration. It is really a great addition to my martial arts arsenal. I am learning a thing our two from it.
